<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
  <%- include('partials/head', { titulo: 'Quem Somos' }) %>
  <style>

    /* ═══════════════════════════════════════════
       HERO VÍDEO — CINEMA FULLSCREEN
    ═══════════════════════════════════════════ */

    .hero-sobre {
      position: relative;
      width: 100%;
      height: 96vh;
      min-height: 580px;
      overflow: hidden;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .hero-video {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      filter: brightness(0.32) contrast(1.10);
      z-index: 1;
      transform: scale(1.04);
      transition: transform 8s ease;
    }

    .hero-sobre:hover .hero-video {
      transform: scale(1.00);
    }

    .hero-overlay {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      z-index: 2;
      background:
        linear-gradient(to bottom,
          rgba(0,0,0,0.20) 0%,
          rgba(0,0,0,0.05) 40%,
          rgba(0,0,0,0.55) 100%);
    }

    .hero-grain {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      z-index: 3;
      opacity: 0.035;
      background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 256 256' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='noise'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23noise)' opacity='1'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
      background-repeat: repeat;
      background-size: 180px;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .hero-content {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 4;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2rem;
      max-width: 900px;
    }

    .hero-label {
      display: inline-block;
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      letter-spacing: 6px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--cor-dourado);
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease 0.3s forwards;
    }

    .hero-title {
      font-family: var(--fonte-titulo);
      font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 7vw, 5.5rem);
      color: #ffffff;
      line-height: 1.05;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeUp 0.9s ease 0.6s forwards;
    }

    .hero-title span {
      color: var(--cor-dourado);
      animation: brilhoTexto 4s ease-in-out 1.5s infinite alternate;
      display: inline-block;
    }

    .hero-desc {
      font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.2rem);
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.80);
      line-height: 1.9;
      max-width: 640px;
      margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeUp 0.9s ease 0.9s forwards;
    }

    .hero-cta {
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeUp 0.9s ease 1.2s forwards;
    }

    .hero-scroll-hint {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 2.5rem;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      z-index: 5;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeUp 1s ease 1.8s forwards;
    }

    .hero-scroll-hint span {
      font-size: 0.65rem;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35);
    }

    .scroll-line {
      width: 1px;
      height: 50px;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--cor-dourado), transparent);
      animation: scrollPulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    @keyframes scrollPulse {
      0%, 100% { opacity: 0.4; transform: scaleY(1); }
      50%       { opacity: 1;   transform: scaleY(1.1); }
    }

    /* ═══════════════════════════════════════════
       MANIFESTO — FRASE IMPACTANTE
    ═══════════════════════════════════════════ */

    .manifesto {
      padding: 6rem 2rem;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .manifesto::before {
      content: '"';
      font-family: var(--fonte-titulo);
      font-size: 18rem;
      color: rgba(255,196,0,0.04);
      position: absolute;
      top: -3rem;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      line-height: 1;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 0;
    }

    .manifesto-texto {
      font-family: var(--fonte-titulo);
      font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3.5vw, 2.4rem);
      color: var(--cor-fonte);
      max-width: 820px;
      margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
      line-height: 1.55;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .manifesto-texto strong {
      color: var(--cor-dourado);
    }

    .manifesto-assinatura {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--cor-dourado);
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .manifesto-assinatura::before {
      content: '';
      display: inline-block;
      width: 36px;
      height: 1px;
      background: var(--cor-dourado);
      vertical-align: middle;
      margin-right: 12px;
    }

    .manifesto-assinatura::after {
      content: '';
      display: inline-block;
      width: 36px;
      height: 1px;
      background: var(--cor-dourado);
      vertical-align: middle;
      margin-left: 12px;
    }

    /* ═══════════════════════════════════════════
       HISTÓRIA — SPLIT LAYOUT
    ═══════════════════════════════════════════ */

    .historia {
      padding: 5rem 0 6rem;
    }

    .historia-inner {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 5rem;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .historia-img-wrap {
      position: relative;
    }

    .historia-img-frame {
      position: relative;
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .historia-img-frame img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 560px;
      object-fit: cover;
      object-position: center top;
      filter: brightness(0.80) contrast(1.05) saturate(0.90);
      transition: filter 0.8s ease, transform 0.8s ease;
      display: block;
    }

    .historia-img-wrap:hover .historia-img-frame img {
      filter: brightness(0.92) contrast(1.05) saturate(1.0);
      transform: scale(1.02);
    }

    .historia-img-borda {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 18px 0 0 18px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,196,0,0.20);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      z-index: -1;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .historia-badge {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 2rem;
      right: -1.5rem;
      background: var(--cor-dourado);
      color: #000;
      padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
      border-radius: var(--radius-md);
      font-family: var(--fonte-titulo);
      text-align: center;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(255,196,0,0.30);
      z-index: 2;
    }

    .historia-badge span {
      display: block;
      font-size: 2.2rem;
      line-height: 1;
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .historia-badge small {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-family: var(--fonte-principal);
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .historia-texto {
      padding-right: 1rem;
    }

    .historia-label {
      font-size: 0.70rem;
      letter-spacing: 5px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--cor-dourado);
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .historia-titulo {
      font-family: var(--fonte-titulo);
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem);
      color: var(--cor-fonte);
      line-height: 1.2;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .historia-titulo span {
      color: var(--cor-dourado);
      animation: brilhoTexto 4s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
      display: inline-block;
    }

    .historia-p {
      color: #b8b8b8;
      line-height: 1.95;
      font-size: 1.02rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    }

    .historia-detalhe {
      display: flex;
      gap: 2rem;
      margin: 2.5rem 0;
      padding-top: 2rem;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,196,0,0.10);
    }

    .historia-detalhe-item {
      flex: 1;
    }

    .historia-detalhe-item strong {
      display: block;
      font-family: var(--fonte-titulo);
      font-size: 1.6rem;
      color: var(--cor-dourado);
      margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
    }

    .historia-detalhe-item small {
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      letter-spacing: 1.5px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: #666;
    }

    /* ═══════════════════════════════════════════
       VÍDEO EM DESTAQUE — SEÇÃO CINEMA
    ═══════════════════════════════════════════ */

    .video-destaque {
      padding: 5rem 0;
      position: relative;
    }

    .video-destaque::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.40);
      z-index: -1;
    }

    .video-destaque-header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
    }

    .video-destaque-header .secao-label {
      font-size: 0.70rem;
      letter-spacing: 5px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--cor-dourado);
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .video-destaque-header h2 {
      font-family: var(--fonte-titulo);
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem);
      color: var(--cor-fonte);
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .video-destaque-header p {
      color: #888;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .video-frame {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      position: relative;
    }

    .video-frame-inner {
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      overflow: hidden;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,196,0,0.15);
      box-shadow:
        0 0 0 1px rgba(255,196,0,0.06),
        0 30px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.60),
        0 0 60px rgba(255,196,0,0.06);
      position: relative;
      background: #000;
    }

    .video-frame-inner video {
      width: 100%;
      display: block;
      max-height: 520px;
      object-fit: contain;
    }

    .video-frame-brilho {
      position: absolute;
      inset: -2px;
      border-radius: calc(var(--radius-lg) + 2px);
      background: linear-gradient(135deg,
        rgba(255,196,0,0.08),
        transparent 40%,
        transparent 60%,
        rgba(255,196,0,0.04));
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 2;
    }

    .video-legenda {
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
      text-align: center;
      color: #555;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }

    .video-legenda i {
      color: var(--cor-dourado);
      margin-right: 6px;
    }

    /* ═══════════════════════════════════════════
       STATS — NÚMEROS QUE IMPRESSIONAM
    ═══════════════════════════════════════════ */

    .stats {
      padding: 6rem 0;
    }

    .stats-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 0;
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .stat-item {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
      position: relative;
    }

    .stat-item:not(:last-child)::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      right: 0;
      top: 25%;
      height: 50%;
      width: 1px;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom,
        transparent,
        rgba(255,196,0,0.18),
        transparent);
    }

    .stat-numero {
      font-family: var(--fonte-titulo);
      font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 5vw, 4rem);
      color: var(--cor-dourado);
      display: block;
      line-height: 1;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      animation: brilhoTexto 4s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
    }

    .stat-label {
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: #555;
      display: block;
    }

    /* ═══════════════════════════════════════════
       VALORES
    ═══════════════════════════════════════════ */

    .valores {
      padding: 5rem 0 6rem;
    }

    .valores-header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 4rem;
    }

    .secao-label {
      font-size: 0.70rem;
      letter-spacing: 5px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--cor-dourado);
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .secao-titulo {
      font-family: var(--fonte-titulo);
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.6rem);
      color: var(--cor-fonte);
    }

    .valores-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .valor-card {
      padding: 3rem 2rem;
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      background: var(--cor-bg-card);
      border: 1px solid var(--cor-borda);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      text-align: center;
      transition: var(--transicao);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .valor-card::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      opacity: 0;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at 50% 0, rgba(255,196,0,0.08), transparent 65%);
      transition: opacity 0.5s ease;
    }

    .valor-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-8px);
      border-color: rgba(255,196,0,0.22);
      box-shadow: 0 24px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.35), 0 0 30px rgba(255,196,0,0.08);
    }

    .valor-card:hover::before {
      opacity: 1;
    }

    .valor-icone {
      width: 68px;
      height: 68px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: rgba(255,196,0,0.08);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,196,0,0.18);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      margin: 0 auto 1.75rem;
      font-size: 1.6rem;
      color: var(--cor-dourado);
      transition: var(--transicao);
    }

    .valor-card:hover .valor-icone {
      background: rgba(255,196,0,0.15);
      box-shadow: 0 0 22px rgba(255,196,0,0.20);
    }

    .valor-card h4 {
      font-family: var(--fonte-titulo);
      color: var(--cor-dourado);
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .valor-card p {
      color: #888;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      line-height: 1.75;
    }

    /* ═══════════════════════════════════════════
       CTA FINAL
    ═══════════════════════════════════════════ */

    .cta-final {
      padding: 7rem 2rem;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .cta-final::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 50%;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translate(-50%,-50%);
      width: 600px;
      height: 600px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,196,0,0.06), transparent 65%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .cta-final h2 {
      font-family: var(--fonte-titulo);
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.2rem);
      color: var(--cor-dourado);
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
      animation: brilhoTexto 4s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
    }

    .cta-final p {
      color: #888;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      max-width: 480px;
      margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    /* ═══════════════════════════════════════════
       SCROLL REVEAL
    ═══════════════════════════════════════════ */

    .reveal {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(36px);
      transition: opacity 0.85s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1),
                  transform 0.85s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
    }

    .reveal.reveal--left {
      transform: translateX(-40px);
    }

    .reveal.reveal--right {
      transform: translateX(40px);
    }

    .reveal.visible {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translate(0);
    }

    .reveal-delay-1 { transition-delay: 0.10s; }
    .reveal-delay-2 { transition-delay: 0.22s; }
    .reveal-delay-3 { transition-delay: 0.34s; }
    .reveal-delay-4 { transition-delay: 0.46s; }

    /* ═══════════════════════════════════════════
       RESPONSIVIDADE
    ═══════════════════════════════════════════ */

    @media (max-width: 1024px) {
      .historia-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3rem; }
      .historia-badge { right: 1rem; bottom: 1rem; }
      .historia-texto { padding-right: 0; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .stats-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
      .stat-item:nth-child(2)::after { display: none; }
      .valores-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 576px) {
      .historia-img-borda { display: none; }
      .historia-detalhe { flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; }
      .stats-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
      .stat-item::after { display: none !important; }
      .valores-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .manifesto::before { font-size: 10rem; }
      .hero-sobre { height: 80vh; }
    }

  </style>
</head>

<body data-bs-theme="dark">

  <%- include('partials/navbar', { paginaAtiva: 'sobre' }) %>


  <!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════
       HERO — VÍDEO CINEMA
  ══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="hero-sobre">
    <video class="hero-video" autoplay muted loop playsinline preload="auto">
      <source src="/assets/videos/sobre.mp4" type="video/mp4">
    </video>
    <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
    <div class="hero-grain"></div>

    <div class="hero-content">
      <span class="hero-label">Studio Patty Leão · Parque Bologne</span>
      <h1 class="hero-title">
        Mais que um salão —<br>
        um lar de <span>transformação</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="hero-desc">
        Cada cliente que cruza nossa porta merece sair mais linda,
        mais confiante e com o coração mais leve do que entrou.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-cta">
        <a href="/agendamento" class="btn-dourado text-decoration-none">
          <i class="fas fa-calendar-check me-2"></i>AGENDE SEU HORÁRIO
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="hero-scroll-hint">
      <span>role</span>
      <div class="scroll-line"></div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════
       MANIFESTO
  ══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="manifesto reveal">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="manifesto-texto">
        Acreditamos que beleza não é sobre perfeição —
        é sobre <strong>ser a melhor versão de si mesma</strong>,
        com cuidado, autenticidade e a confiança
        de quem sabe que está em boas mãos.
      </p>
      <span class="manifesto-assinatura">Patty Leão</span>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════
       HISTÓRIA DA PATTY
  ══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="historia">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="historia-inner">

        <!-- IMAGEM -->
        <div class="historia-img-wrap reveal reveal--left">
          <div class="historia-img-frame">
            <img src="/assets/img/modelo_cabelo.jpg" alt="Studio Patty Leão">
          </div>
          <div class="historia-img-borda"></div>
          <div class="historia-badge">
            <span>4+</span>
            <small>Anos de<br>experiência</small>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- TEXTO -->
        <div class="historia-texto reveal reveal--right">
          <span class="historia-label">Nossa história</span>
          <h2 class="historia-titulo">
            A paixão da <span>Patty Leão</span><br>
            que virou um studio
          </h2>
          <p class="historia-p">
            Com mais de 4 anos de experiência no universo da beleza, Patty Leão
            fundou o Studio com um sonho simples e poderoso: fazer com que cada
            mulher que sai daqui se sinta mais bonita, confiante e especial do
            que quando entrou.
          </p>
          <p class="historia-p">
            Especializada em progressivas, tratamentos capilares e técnicas de
            colorimetria, Patty construiu uma clientela fiel a base de dedicação,
            cuidado real e resultados que encantam — cabelo por cabelo,
            atendimento por atendimento.
          </p>
          <p class="historia-p">
            Hoje o Studio é referência no Jardim Solange e região, combinando
            atendimento humanizado com tecnologia de ponta. Um espaço onde
            você não é mais um número na agenda — você é a protagonista.
          </p>

          <div class="historia-detalhe">
            <div class="historia-detalhe-item">
              <strong>300+</strong>
              <small>Clientes fiéis</small>
            </div>
            <div class="historia-detalhe-item">
              <strong>98%</strong>
              <small>Satisfação</small>
            </div>
            <div class="historia-detalhe-item">
              <strong>4</strong>
              <small>Especialidades</small>
            </div>
          </div>

          <a href="/agendamento" class="btn-dourado text-decoration-none d-inline-flex align-items-center gap-2">
            <i class="fas fa-calendar-check"></i> AGENDAR AGORA
          </a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════
       VÍDEO EM DESTAQUE
  ══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="video-destaque" style="background: rgba(0,0,0,0.50);">
    <div class="container">

      <div class="video-destaque-header reveal">
        <span class="secao-label">Studio em movimento</span>
        <h2>O Studio Patty Leão por dentro</h2>
        <p>Veja a magia acontecer — cada transformação começa aqui.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="video-frame reveal reveal-delay-1">
